  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doodle Harmony Idle Merge is a relaxing idle merging game, where you buy Doodles and generate them in real time, then sell them to turn a profit or keep them around to earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.poster.avif?t=1728917589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.webm?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.mp4?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨Doodle Merging: Merge two identical Doodles to upgrade them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 Passive Income Generation: Your Doodles earn money for you automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄Offline Progress: Keep earning money even when you're not playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔓Unlock New Doodles: Explore a variety of characters to merge and expand your Collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆Achievements: Unlock achievements as you progress through the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📻Radio System: Radio System to choose your music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌑Dark Mode: Chose between a light mode and a dark mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚙️ Upgrades: Enhance your gameplay with upgrades!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🛠️ Skills: Use special skills that speed up your progression in the game!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.poster.avif?t=1728917589\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.webm?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.mp4?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doodle Harmony Idle Merge is a relaxing idle merging game, where you buy Doodles and generate them in real time, then sell them to turn a profit or keep them around to earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.poster.avif?t=1728917589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.webm?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/e576e8530bc8ab3dcc0d38cef267dfb7.mp4?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨Doodle Merging: Merge two identical Doodles to upgrade them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 Passive Income Generation: Your Doodles earn money for you automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔄Offline Progress: Keep earning money even when you're not playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔓Unlock New Doodles: Explore a variety of characters to merge and expand your Collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆Achievements: Unlock achievements as you progress through the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📻Radio System: Radio System to choose your music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌑Dark Mode: Chose between a light mode and a dark mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚙️ Upgrades: Enhance your gameplay with upgrades!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🛠️ Skills: Use special skills that speed up your progression in the game!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.poster.avif?t=1728917589\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.webm?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/f4ade4a253be3bdfb4452a7e2e28705b.mp4?t=1728917589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
